import React from 'react'

import {
    Row,
    Col,
    Nav,
    Image,
} from 'react-bootstrap';
const LOGO = require('../assets/images/login/logo.png');

export default function Navbar() {
    return (
        <Nav
            activeKey="/home"
            onSelect={(selectedKey) => alert(`selected ${selectedKey}`)}
            // className="justify-content-between mx-0 pt-0"
            style={{backgroundColor: 'white'}}
        >
                        
            <Col lg={1} />

                <Col lg={5}>
                    <Row>
                        <Col className="d-flex" lg={3}>
                            <Image src={LOGO} className={"m-auto p-3"} />
                        </Col>


                        <Col lg={9}  className="d-flex">
                            <Row className={"mt-auto p-3"}>
                                <Nav.Item>
                                    <Nav.Link href="/home" className="landing-menu-title">What is Imodo</Nav.Link>
                                </Nav.Item>
                                
                                <Nav.Item >
                                    <Nav.Link  eventKey="link-10" className="landing-menu-title">How to use it</Nav.Link>
                                </Nav.Item>

                                <Nav.Item>
                                    <Nav.Link eventKey="link-1" className="landing-menu-title">For developpers</Nav.Link>
                                </Nav.Item>
                            </Row>
                        </Col>
                    </Row>
                </Col>

                <Col lg={5} className="d-flex">
                    <Row className={"my-auto ml-auto p-3"}>
                        <Nav.Item>
                            {/* <Button variant="danger">Login</Button> */}
                            <Facebook content="Login" />
                        </Nav.Item>
                        {/* <Nav.Item>
                            <Form>
                                <Form.Group controlId="exampleForm.ControlSelect1">
                                    <Form.Control as="select">
                                        <option>1</option>
                                        <option>2</option>
                                        <option>3</option>
                                        <option>4</option>
                                        <option>5</option>
                                    </Form.Control>
                                </Form.Group>
                            </Form>
                        </Nav.Item> 
                        */}
                    </Row>
                </Col>
            
            <Col lg={1} />

        </Nav>
    )
}
